{"tid":722923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【週末治癒大帖】中國生活之日常","createTime":"2018-06-30T03:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T18:30:41.000Z","uid":131691,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dcf3112ea6352229bfe3531625ea10f36e18737c","tid":722923,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:18:01.000Z","msg":"如果你對昆蟲生命有同情心，請音速離開本帖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/111737_49fe2c6b72bd1b288aa8a402797e4250.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F111737_49fe2c6b72bd1b288aa8a402797e4250.gif&h=9a99b1c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上回分解：交通篇 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/713603/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/713603/</a><br />\n<br />\n原本4chan啲webm細filesize好多，奈何連登淨係支援gif... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由原本60fps變10fps再加giflossy壓縮，如果唔係load死大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登又限制最大個filesize得10MB，所以我用mixtape.moe upload算<br />\n廢話少講，我哋開始呢個weekend嘅【中國治癒】thread<br />\n<br />\n首先，補貼返5個因爲太大所以上個禮拜post唔到嘅：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://my.mixtape.moe/fugtob.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.mixtape.moe%2Ffugtob.gif&h=1f408efb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ac5d04cfb27d536bfbcd3fc3f96b0d3336ed318","tid":722923,"uid":131691,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://my.mixtape.moe/yenkmd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.mixtape.moe%2Fyenkmd.gif&h=c55ed509&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbc758298cd5f4f42adc23169b91b38d1b03869f","tid":722923,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://my.mixtape.moe/vguiga.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.mixtape.moe%2Fvguiga.gif&h=5af989eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"416247629d5ff657e149b16925052376b93aa11e","tid":722923,"uid":131691,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://my.mixtape.moe/uuvzds.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.mixtape.moe%2Fuuvzds.gif&h=5578c03f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b994d8dfef6809f5cb47bbabe0b60941f91b16b0","tid":722923,"uid":131691,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://my.mixtape.moe/uvxdje.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.mixtape.moe%2Fuvxdje.gif&h=3be16bac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1212b65546024213b0d9585cde9aac39b9af379a","tid":722923,"uid":131691,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:27:11.000Z","msg":"好！我哋入正題。<br />\n<br />\n呢個禮拜嘅主題係「生活」。<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅生活如果問大家，我諗大家都會答行商場呀，同朋友聚餐呀嗰啲。辛苦完一個禮拜，一定要去休息一下嘅！有人會去聽concert，有人會去行山，有人會落旺角機舖打鋪機，有人會上Hong Kong Club食返個buffet，人各有志。<br />\n<br />\n中國呢？首先會斬人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://my.mixtape.moe/jvfkvr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.mixtape.moe%2Fjvfkvr.gif&h=99972554&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71dacdb7e1fe631c2c23c8f23b01c00f1c88083d","tid":722923,"uid":131691,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://my.mixtape.moe/lpsxbd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.mixtape.moe%2Flpsxbd.gif&h=8e8f26da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b058095aff6d82d43fc4123dc3e58641cb6ef82c","tid":722923,"uid":131691,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T03:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/125456_512c07727d00c16c5acf35feeb6e5898.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F125456_512c07727d00c16c5acf35feeb6e5898.gif&h=2d945691